<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="exhibition-n">exhibition <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌeksɪ'bɪʃn/    美 /ˌeksɪ'bɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>展览；展出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>put sth on exhibition 
展出某物</p></div>

<h4 id="2-bre">2.★ <strong>(BrE) 展览品；展览会：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We are organizing an art exhibition for high school students in the city. 
我们在为本市的高中学生组织艺术展。</p><footer>2008 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Xi'an International <strong><em>_</em></strong>_(展览) Center has attracted many business people.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. Exhibition  </p></div>